<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>智能医疗陪护系统 - 核心功能详解</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
            background: #f0f4f8;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.07);
        }
        
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #3b82f6 50%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .emergency-red { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%); }
        .urgent-yellow { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%); }
        .normal-green { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); }
        
        .pulse-ring {
            animation: pulse-ring 2s cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1) infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse-ring {
            0% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.7); }
            70% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 0 20px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0); }
            100% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(239, 68, 68, 0); }
        }
        
        .wave-bg {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.4;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 40% 20%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .chat-bubble {
            animation: slideIn 0.3s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes slideIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        
        .typing-dot {
            animation: typing 1.4s infinite ease-in-out both;
        }
        
        .typing-dot:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: -0.32s; }
        .typing-dot:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: -0.16s; }
        
        @keyframes typing {
            0%, 80%, 100% { transform: scale(0); }
            40% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        
        .nav-path {
            stroke-dasharray: 1000;
            stroke-dashoffset: 1000;
            animation: drawPath 3s ease-in-out forwards;
        }
        
        @keyframes drawPath {
            to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
        }
        
        .medical-cross {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            clip-path: polygon(20% 0%, 80% 0%, 80% 20%, 100% 20%, 100% 80%, 80% 80%, 80% 100%, 20% 100%, 20% 80%, 0% 80%, 0% 20%, 20% 20%);
        }
        
        .tab-active {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .confidence-bar {
            transition: width 1s ease-out;
        }
        
        .fade-in {
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-800">

    <div class="wave-bg"></div>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 glass-panel border-b border-white/20">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 medical-cross flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i data-lucide="activity" class="text-white w-6 h-6"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800">MediCare AI</h1>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">智能医疗陪护系统 3.2</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <nav class="hidden md:flex gap-8">
                <button onclick="scrollToSection('triage')" class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">智能导诊</button>
                <button onclick="scrollToSection('previsit')" class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">诊前预问诊</button>
                <button onclick="scrollToSection('accompaniment')" class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">诊中陪护</button>
                <button onclick="scrollToSection('postcare')" class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">诊后关怀</button>
            </nav>
            <button class="md:hidden" onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">
                <i data-lucide="menu" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 mb-6 fade-in">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-700">AI 驱动的全流程医疗陪护</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
                让每一次就医<br>
                <span class="gradient-text">都安心、高效、温暖</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
                融合多模态AI技术，覆盖诊前、诊中、诊后全周期，为患者提供智能导诊、预问诊、实时陪护与康复管理服务
            </p>
            
            <!-- Feature Navigation Tabs -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-16 fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
                <button onclick="activateFeature(0)" class="feature-tab px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-slate-100 flex items-center gap-2 group">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg emergency-red flex items-center justify-center text-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i data-lucide="siren" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-medium">安全为先</span>
                </button>
                <button onclick="activateFeature(1)" class="feature-tab px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-slate-100 flex items-center gap-2 group">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-400 flex items-center justify-center text-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i data-lucide="clipboard-list" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-medium">效率提升</span>
                </button>
                <button onclick="activateFeature(2)" class="feature-tab px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-slate-100 flex items-center gap-2 group">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-400 flex items-center justify-center text-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i data-lucide="ear" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-medium">知情保障</span>
                </button>
                <button onclick="activateFeature(3)" class="feature-tab px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-slate-100 flex items-center gap-2 group">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg normal-green flex items-center justify-center text-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i data-lucide="heart-handshake" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-medium">持续陪伴</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Feature 1: 智能导诊 (Safety First) -->
    <section id="triage" class="py-20 px-6 relative">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl emergency-red flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg shadow-red-200">
                            <i data-lucide="shield-alert" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">智能导诊</h2>
                            <p class="text-red-600 font-medium">安全为先 · 分级诊疗</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        患者描述症状或上传伤口照片，AI通过规则树判断急诊级别。当置信度低于90%时，自动转接人工远程陪护，确保不漏诊、不误诊。
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/60 border border-white">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                                <span class="text-red-600 font-bold text-sm">1</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">多模态症状采集</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">支持文字描述、语音输入、伤口照片AI识别</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/60 border border-white">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                                <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold text-sm">2</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">智能分级分诊</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">红色（危急）/ 黄色（紧急）/ 绿色（普通）三级预警</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/60 border border-white">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                                <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm">3</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">院内导航规划</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">自动推荐最优科室并生成实时导航路径</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Interactive Demo -->
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="glass-panel rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-2xl">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
                                    <i data-lucide="bot" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800">AI 导诊助手</h3>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">在线 | 响应时间 < 1s</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex gap-2">
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-xs font-medium flex items-center gap-1">
                                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                                    系统正常
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Chat Interface -->
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-4 h-96 overflow-y-auto mb-4 space-y-4" id="triageChat">
                            <div class="chat-bubble flex gap-3">
                                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                                    <i data-lucide="bot" class="w-4 h-4 text-white"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none shadow-sm max-w-[80%]">
                                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">您好，我是智能导诊助手。请描述您的症状，或上传患处照片，我将为您评估紧急程度并推荐科室。</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Input Area -->
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <button class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 transition-colors text-slate-600">
                                <i data-lucide="camera" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                            </button>
                            <input type="text" id="symptomInput" placeholder="描述您的症状..." 
                                class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 text-sm"
                                onkeypress="if(event.key==='Enter') simulateTriage()">
                            <button onclick="simulateTriage()" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium transition-colors">
                                发送
                            </button>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Triage Result Panel (Hidden by default) -->
                        <div id="triageResult" class="hidden mt-4 p-4 rounded-xl border-l-4 bg-white shadow-lg transform transition-all">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg" id="triageLevel">评估结果</h4>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1" id="triageDesc">建议立即就诊</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-right">
                                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold" id="confidenceScore">95%</div>
                                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">置信度</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-full bg-slate-200 rounded-full h-2 mb-3">
                                <div id="confidenceBar" class="confidence-bar h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500" style="width: 0%"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex gap-2 mt-4">
                                <button class="flex-1 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
                                    查看导航路径
                                </button>
                                <button id="humanEscalateBtn" class="hidden flex-1 py-2 rounded-lg bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-orange-200 transition-colors">
                                    转接人工陪护
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Decorative Elements -->
                    <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-24 h-24 bg-red-100 rounded-full blur-2xl opacity-60"></div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-100 rounded-full blur-2xl opacity-60"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Feature 2: 诊前预问诊 (Efficiency) -->
    <section id="previsit" class="py-20 px-6 bg-white/50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <!-- Interactive Report Demo -->
                <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 relative">
                    <div class="glass-panel rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-2xl bg-white">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6 border-b border-slate-100 pb-4">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-lg">智能预问诊报告</h3>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">生成时间: 2026-04-09 14:30</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex gap-2">
                                <button class="p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 text-slate-600">
                                    <i data-lucide="download" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                                </button>
                                <button class="p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 text-slate-600">
                                    <i data-lucide="share-2" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
                                    <i data-lucide="user" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex-1">
                                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">患者</p>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800">张先生 (35岁)</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-right">
                                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">预约科室</p>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-blue-600">消化内科</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100">
                                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1">主诉症状</p>
                                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800">上腹部疼痛3天，伴有反酸</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100">
                                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1">既往病史</p>
                                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800">慢性胃炎 (2019年确诊)</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100">
                                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1">过敏史</p>
                                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-green-600">无已知过敏</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100">
                                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1">当前用药</p>
                                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800">奥美拉唑 20mg qd</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                    <i data-lucide="alert-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-600"></i>
                                    <span class="font-semibold text-amber-800 text-sm">AI 问诊摘要</span>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-sm text-amber-900 leading-relaxed">
                                    患者自述餐后疼痛加重，夜间偶有痛醒。无呕血黑便，体重无明显下降。建议完善胃镜检查，排除溃疡可能。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4 border-t border-slate-100">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse"></div>
                                <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">已推送至诊室终端</span>
                            </div>
                            <button class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-medium hover:underline">查看双语版本 (EN/CN)</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-400 flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-200">
                            <i data-lucide="zap" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">诊前预问诊</h2>
                            <p class="text-blue-600 font-medium">效率提升 · 结构化报告</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        AI主动询问病史、过敏史、当前用药情况，自动生成结构化双语问诊报告，在患者见到医生前推送至诊室，节省面诊时间30%以上。
                    </p>

                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="feature-card p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                                <i data-lucide="message-square" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500"></i>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">智能对话采集</h4>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">自然语言处理技术，引导患者完整描述病情，自动提取关键医学信息</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                                <i data-lucide="file-text" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500"></i>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">结构化病历生成</h4>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">符合HL7标准的电子病历格式，支持中文/英文双语切换</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                                <i data-lucide="send" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500"></i>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">实时同步诊室</h4>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">医生提前了解病情，面诊时直接切入重点，提升诊疗效率</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Feature 3: 诊中陪护 (Informed Consent) -->
    <section id="accompaniment" class="py-20 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
